data.description: Charming traditional two story home in the heart of Newberg. Bright, open floor plan with formal dining room, family room, and living room with built-ins and gas fireplace. Four bedrooms, plus large loft/bonus room. Bright and inviting main floor den with french doors. Upstairs primary suite with dual sinks, soaking tub, and shower. This is a must see in a great neighborhood close to parks, shopping, and schools.
